EN: In this high-altitude area, you can see many snow-capped mountains.

ZH: 海拔越高，气温越低。
EN: The higher the altitude, the lower the temperature.

ZH: 在这座城市，最高点的海拔超过3000米。
EN: In this city, the highest point has an altitude of over 3000 meters.

